cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.ST, cs.NE 

The paper deals with the application of deep learning models for high-dimensional process monitoring, specifically using deep probabilistic autoencoders. This falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the use of unsupervised learning (cs.AI) and statistical methods (cs.ST) for monitoring. Finally, the use of deep learning models such as autoencoders falls under the category of neural networks (cs.NE).
